Select 
vbpa.lifnr,
COUNT(VBRK.KUNAG) AS Qtd_Cliente
from vbrk vbrk
inner join vbrp vbrp on vbrk.vbeln = vbrp.vbeln
inner join vbpa vbpa on vbpa.vbeln = vbrk.vbeln
where vbpa.parvw = 'TL' and vbrp.kowrr <> 'Y' 
group by vbpa.lifnr    
having COUNT(VBRK.KUNAG) >= 4

--Serverless 1:03 
--dedicado 100 dwu 6seg

SELECT vbpa.lifnr,
       vbrp.matnr,
       vbrk.vtweg,
       Sum( cast ( Replace(  vbrp.netwr   , ',', '.') as float)) AS SOMA_NETWR,
       Sum( cast (Replace(  vbrp.kzwi2  , ',', '.') as float)) AS soma_kzwi2,
       Sum( cast (Replace(vbrp.kzwi5  , ',', '.') as float)) AS soma_kzwi5,
       Sum( cast (Replace (vbrp.kzwi6 , ',', '.') as float)) AS soma_kzwi6
FROM   vbrk vbrk
       INNER JOIN vbrp vbrp
               ON vbrk.vbeln = vbrp.vbeln
       INNER JOIN vbpa vbpa
               ON vbpa.vbeln = vbrk.vbeln
WHERE  vbpa.parvw = 'TL'
       AND vbrp.kowrr <> 'Y'
GROUP  BY vbpa.lifnr,
          vbrp.matnr,
          vbrk.vtweg
